<dl> <dt><span class="script">template.XULAttr("image")</span></dt> <dd>Type: <em>URI</em></dd> <dd>The URI of the image to appear on the element. If this attribute is empty or left out, no image appears. The position of the image is determined by the <span class="script">template.XULAttr("dir")</span> and <span class="script">template.XULAttr("orient")</span> attributes.</dd>
</dl>
